item.title: WIP Wednesday: Snowfall Mittens
item.description: WIP stands for a “work in progress.” As an avid crafter, I always have at least one WIP! Yarn: Loops and Threads Urban (Rust) Pattern: Snowfall Mittens Snowfall Mittens I have finished one half of my Christmas present to one of my cousins. I’ve had this yarn sitting in my stash for a long time (I bought it a year and a half ago).
